          "A^2-B^2" "B^2-A^2" "|A^2+B^2|" "|A^2-B^2|" "A^3+B^3" "A^3-B^3" "B^3-A^3" \
          "|A^3+B^3|" "|A^3-B^3|" "real(z)" "real(z) 2" "real(z) 3" \
          "real(z) 4" "imag(z)" "imag(z) 2" "imag(z) 3" "imag(z) 4" \
          "quotient 3" "quotient 4" "quotient 5" "quotient 6" "quotient 7" "quotient 8" \
